data.description: Welcome to your dream home!  This exquisite 4 bed, 2.5 bath home boasts just under 2,100 square feet of living space, with a serene lakeside setting and a uniquely huge lot for this community.  Meticulously remodeled with a keen eye for detail, this home is a true gem!  As you step inside, crown molding graces the ceiling with beautiful tile on the bottom floor and African Chestnut hardwood upstairs.  The kitchen was stunningly remodeled, in full, in 2022, including new appliances.  A new roof in 2023, new washer and dryer, and 2-year-old A/C are icing on the cake.  The home is fully impact glass all the way around-windows and doors.  A 2-car garage with storage as well as a vast amount of closet space on the interior complete the package.  Nautica Isles West offers a wealth of amenities including basketball, volleyball, tennis, clubhouse, tot lot, soccer field, a fully equipped gym, and a sparkling community pool.  Not to mention a manned guard gate and patrolling security.  Living in Nautica Isles West means you're part of a great school zone, and the nearby beaches are just a short drive away. This family-friendly community is a wonderful place to call home, with everything you need for a fulfilling and enjoyable lifestyle.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this incredible home your own!
